2d:{"title":"Our Story","content":"Aiyoflow Media was founded on a simple belief: the best brand strategies come from a deep understanding of culture. Rather than following trends, we identify movements before they peak, and position brands to lead conversations.\n\nWe are not a busy agency. We are a tight, founder-led team with an expansive network of collaborators. This model lets us deliver strategic depth without the overhead.","founder":"$2e"}
31:{"title":"Editorial Thinking","description":"We come from publishing and media. We know how to tell stories that matter and position them for cultural relevance."}
32:{"title":"Creator Intelligence","description":"We understand the creator economy deeply. We build authentic partnerships, not transactional sponsored posts."}
33:{"title":"Global Perspective","description":"We work across markets - US, China, and beyond. We understand nuance and cultural context."}
34:{"title":"Structured Creativity","description":"We are creative, but systematic. Every campaign has measurable objectives and a documented process."}
